videos.description: Chicago Sky's Candace Parker rejects Connecticut's Jasmine Thomas with an emphatic block.
videos.headline: Candace Parker comes up with huge block on Jasmine Thomas

videos.description: Courtney Vandersloot delivers a pinpoint pass to Astou Ndour-Fall, who finishes with an acrobatic layup.
videos.headline: Vandersloot dishes no-look pass to Ndour-Fall for the layup

videos.description: Diamond DeShields nets a three-pointer before halftime to put the Sky back on top.
videos.headline: DeShields beats buzzer to give Sky a 1-point lead at the half

videos.description: Stefanie Dolson puts the Chicago Sky up by six with a three-point shot from distance.
videos.headline: Dolson caps off 7-0 Sky run with deep three-pointer

videos.description: Briann January helps the Connecticut Sun inch closer to the Chicago Sky with a three-point play.
videos.headline: January hits huge and-1 to bring Sun within a point

videos.description: DeWanna Bonner's game-winning shot rims out as the Connecticut Sun and Chicago Sky go to overtime.
videos.headline: Bonner can't hit winner as Sun-Sky go to OT

videos.description: Courtney Vandersloot threads the needle on two separate occasions to help the Sky win Game 1 of the WNBA semifinals.
videos.headline: Vandersloot's clutch assists lead Sky to double-OT win over Sun

videos.description: Courtney Vandersloot tallies the second playoff triple-double in WNBA history to help the Sky beat the Sun in Game 1 of the WNBA semifinals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Highlight (Chicago Sky win 2OT thriller behind Vandersloot's historic triple-double) 2021/9/28 ESHEET SC
